4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to equip them with essential skills for a career in cybersecurity. The program lasts 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Students will gain expertise in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, as well as cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by multiple institutions. The curriculum is available in English and Spanish. 

